1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,200
Hey, Nishikata. What are you doing?

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,500
N-Nothing! I'm not doing anything.

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,300
Is there something written on that eraser?

4
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,800
Huh? There's nothing written! Don't look!

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:26,500
The more you hide it, the more curious I get, you know.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,200
I'm not hiding anything! It's just a regular eraser.

7
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:36,500
Then you wouldn't mind showing me, right?

8
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,000
N-No way! Absolutely not!

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,500
Did you know that if you write the name
of the person you like on an eraser, they'll like you back?

10
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:51,200
I-I don't believe in stuff like that!

11
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Your face is turning red, Nishikata.

12
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,800
It's not red! It's just hot in here!

13
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:05,500
It's not that hot today, though.

14
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:10,300
Geez... Takagi-san, you're always teasing me.

15
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,500
I'm not teasing you. You're just funny, Nishikata.

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:20,800
The teacher's coming. You should put that eraser away, don't you think?

17
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,500
Oh no! Where did I put it?

18
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:30,000
Here, you dropped it.

19
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:34,800
Oh, th-thanks... You didn't look at it, right?

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,500
Hmm, who knows?
